g%20exhibition%2Fstunt%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%3A%20Netflix%20managed%20to%20attract%20the%20kind%20of%20audience%20for%20the%20games%20that%20you'd%20expect%20from%20the%20NFL%2C%20which%20is%20continually%20the%20most%20popular%20thing%20on%20conventional%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20NFL%20and%20the%20streamer%20say%20that%20both%20of%20Wednesday's%20games%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Kansas%20City%20Chiefs%20vs.%20the%20Pittsburgh%20Steelers%20and%20the%20Baltimore%20Ravens%20vs.%20the%20Houston%20Texans%20%E2%80%94%20averaged%20around%2024%20million%20viewers%20in%20the%20US.%20That's%20a%20record%20for%20streaming%20NFL%20games%20in%20the%20country.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E(Those%20initial%20numbers%20may%20swell%20a%20bit%20once%20the%20NFL%2C%20Netflix%2C%20and%20Nielsen%20scour%20for%20additional%20viewers.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20audience%20%E2%80%94%20around%2027%20million%20viewers%20%E2%80%94%20showed%20up%20for%20the%20%26quot%3BBeyonc%C3%A9%20Bowl%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20halftime%20performance%20during%20the%20Ravens%2FTexans%20game%2C%20featuring%2C%20of%20course%2C%20Beyonc%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20comparison%2C%20last%20year%2C%20the%20NFL%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcsports.com%2Fnfl%2Fprofootballtalk%2Frumor-mill%2Fnews%2Fraiders-chiefs-draws-29-million-viewers-for-cbs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eattracted%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20average%20of%20some%2028%20million%20US%20viewers%20for%20the%20two%20games%20it%20broadcast%20on%20Christmas%20Day%2C%20via%20conventional%20TV%20networks.%20(Netflix's%20numbers%20don't%20include%20viewers%20outside%20the%20US%3B%20it%20says%20it%20will%20report%20back%20on%20those%20on%20December%2031.%20Netflix%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.netflix.com%2Ftudum%2Farticles%2Fjake-paul-vs-mike-tyson-live-release-date-news%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520event%2520streamed%2520live%2520on%2Cstreams%2520in%2520the%2520United%2520States.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esays%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20audience%20for%20the%20Tyson%2FPaul%20event%20peaked%20at%2065%20million%20worldwide%20and%2038%20million%20in%20the%20US.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20which%20means%20that%20when%20Netflix%20streams%20Christmas%20games%20again%20next%20year%2C%20and%20again%20in%202027%2C%20it%20won't%20seem%20like%20a%20novelty.%20It%20will%20just%20be%20the%20most%20popular%20sport%20on%20TV%2C%20delivered%20via%20a%20streaming%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20both%20Netflix%20and%20the%20NFL%20want%2C%20for%20slightly%20different%20reasons.%20The%20NFL%20is%20always%20looking%20for%20another%20outlet%20that%20will%20pay%20it%20top%20dollar%20for%20the%20right%20to%20show%20its%20games%20%E2%80%94%20Netflix%20paid%20the%20NFL%20a%20reported%20%24150%20million%20for%20this%20year's%20games%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-nfl-christmas-games-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetflix%20wants%20high-profile%20live%20events%20as%20a%20way%20to%20boost%20its%20nascent%20ad%20business%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWin-win.%20This%20is%20what%20the%20NFL%20has%20been%20finding%20every%20time%20it%20sells%20streaming%20rights%20to%20digital%20players%20over%20the%20years%2C%20including%20Yahoo%2C%20Twitter%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20are%20here%2C%20a%20couple%20other%20notes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20there%20was%20some%20discussion%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fbusiness%2Fmedia%2Fnetflixs-christmas-nfl-playbook-keep-fansand-the-leaguehappy-e7d1ca68%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetflix%20trying%20to%20make%20its%20NFL%20coverage%20unique%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20couldn't%20discern%20anything%20meaningfully%20different%20about%20the%20games%20from%20any%20others%20I've%20watched%20this%20year.%20Which%2C%20again%2C%20is%20the%20point%3A%20The%20NFL%20wants%20the%20product%20to%20look%20the%20same%20no%20matter%20where%20you%20see%