blanket%20is%20available%20in%20all%20bed%20sizes%2C%20but%20we%20particularly%20like%20it%20for%20those%20looking%20for%20a%20large%20king-size%20blanket%20thanks%20to%20dual%20controls%20and%20a%20thin%20but%20warm%20design%20that%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20store%20when%20not%20in%20use.%3Cp%3EJill%20Waldbieser%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize(s)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20throw%2C%20twin%2C%20full%2C%20queen%2C%20and%20king%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20100%25%20polyester%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeat%20Settings%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2012%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAuto%20Shut%20Off%20Timer%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2012-hour%20selectable%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWarranty%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%205-year%20limited%20warranty%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMany%20size%20and%20color%20options%20(king%20and%20queen%20sizes%20have%20dual%20controllers)%2C%20quick%20heating%2C%20Programmable%20auto-shutoff%2C%20long%20cord%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EController%20is%20inconveniently%20placed%2C%20presets%20to%20one%20heat%20and%20auto-off%20setting%2C%20so%20you%20have%20to%20re-set%20those%20each%20time%20you%20turn%20it%20off%20and%20on%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20classic%20Sunbeam%20Royal%20Ultra%20Fleece%20blanket%20is%20like%20a%20favorite%20fleece%20you%20can%20plug%20in%20and%20heat%20up.%20It's%20thin%2C%20which%20is%20great%20because%2C%20at%20this%20size%2C%20anything%20bulky%20would%20be%20a%20chore%20to%20manage%2C%20clean%2C%20and%20store.%20Despite%20its%20size%2C%20however%2C%20it%20warms%20in%20minutes%20and%20consistently%20thanks%20to%20Sunbeam's%20Thermofine%20wiring%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2012%20heating%20settings%2C%20the%20most%20of%20any%20blanket%20we%20tried%2C%20so%20if%20you%20struggle%20to%20find%20the%20just-right%20temperature%2C%20this%20blanket%20could%20be%20a%20good%20choice%20since%20it%20allows%20you%20to%20select%20more%20incrementally.%20An%20adjustable%20auto-off%20timer%20allows%20you%20to%20select%20any%20length%20from%201%20to%2012%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sunbeam%20Royal%20Ultra%20Fleece%20also%20features%20an%20exceptionally%20long%20cord%2C%20which%20gives%20you%20a%20bit%20more%20room%20to%20maneuver.%20This%20is%20especially%20useful%20if%20you%20use%20it%20as%20a%20bedspread%20so%20you%20don't%20get%20tangled%20up%20in%20wiring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20area%20where%20there%20is%20room%20for%20improvement%20is%20the%20controller%2C%20which%20is%20round%20and%20a%20bit%20bulky%20and%20placed%20far%20from%20the%20blanket%20and%20closer%20to%20the%20plug.%20This%20isn't%20ideal%2C%20but%20it%20gets%20the%20job%20done%20well%20for%20a%20basic%2C%20all-purpose%20electric%20blanket%20that%20keeps%20you%20warm%20over%20a%20large%20surface%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20looking%3A%20Beautyrest%20Zuri%20Oversized%20Faux%20Fur%20Heated%20Throw%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Beautyrest%20faux%20fur%20heated%20blanket%20on%20a%20bed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6596fda5ec62ab5daf80b88c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAt%20first%20glance%2C%20you%20wouldn't%20know%20that%20this%20faux%20fur%20design%20from%20Beautyrest%20is%20a%20heated%20throw%20with%20three%20heat%20settings.%3Cp%3EJill%20Waldbieser%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize(s)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2050%26quot%3B%20x%2070%26quot%3B%2C%2050%26quot%3B%20x%2064%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20100%25%20microfiber%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeat%20Settings%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%203%20(85-105%20F)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAuto%20Shut%20Off%20Timer%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%202%20hour%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3C