s.%20That%20doesn't%20detract%20from%20the%20heat%20this%20blanket%20throws%20off%2C%20though.%20Regarding%20performance%2C%20this%20blanket%20was%20one%20of%20our%20tests'%20fastest%20and%20hottest%20heating.%20It%20only%20has%20three%20temperature%20settings%20but%20doesn't%20dip%20below%2070%20degrees%2C%20even%20at%20the%20lowest.%20The%20cord%20is%20a%20comfortable%20length%2C%20and%20the%20controller%20is%20unobtrusive%20and%20easy%20to%20use.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20two-hour%20auto%20shut-off%20that%20works%20flawlessly.%20This%20is%20a%20safe%20bet%20if%20you%20want%20a%20cozy%20electric%20blanket%20that%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20hide%20in%20the%20closet%20between%20uses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20smart%3A%20Sunbeam%20Electric%20Wi-Fi%20Connected%20Loftec%20Electric%20Heated%20Blanket%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Sunbeam%20Connected%20Blanket%20on%20a%20bed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6596ff22ec62ab5daf80b95f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EForget%20reaching%20for%20the%20controller%2C%20the%20Sunbeam%20Connected%20Heated%20Blanket%20lets%20you%20adjust%20the%20heat%20from%20your%20smartphone%20device%20or%20via%20voice%20command.%3Cp%3EJill%20Waldbieser%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize(s)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20twin%2C%20full%2C%20queen%2C%20and%20king%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Polyester%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeat%20Settings%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2010%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAuto%20Shut%20Off%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2010-hour%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWarranty%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%205-year%20limited%20warranty%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Smart%20controls%20allow%20you%20to%20operate%20it%20via%20app%20or%20voice%20control%2C%20preheat%20function%2C%20soft%20feel%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Pricey%2C%20fabric%20does%20tend%20to%20shed%20and%20get%20a%20matted%20look%20after%20a%20while%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sunbeam%20Connected%20Heated%20Blanket%20has%20several%20features%20that%20set%20it%20apart%20from%20the%20other%20blankets%20we%20tested.%20Most%20notably%2C%20it%20can%20be%20controlled%20using%20your%20smartphone%20and%20the%20Sunbeam%20app%20to%20turn%20it%20on%20and%20adjust%20the%20heat%20settings.%20It%20also%20works%20with%20Google%20Assistant%20or%20Alexa%20to%20change%20settings%20using%20voice%20commands.%20That%20alone%20is%20super%20convenient%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can%20preheat%20your%20blanket%20on%20your%20way%20home%20so%20it's%20toasty%20the%20second%20you%20walk%20in%20the%20door%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20larger%20sizes%20of%20this%20blanket%20also%20have%20dual%20temperature%20control%20zones%20so%20if%20you%20have%20two%20sleepers%20under%20it%2C%20each%20can%20set%20their%20preferred%20temperature%20and%20be%20comfortable%2C%20which%20is%20a%20revelation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20the%20app%20also%20allows%20you%20to%20preheat%20your%20blanket%20or%20schedule%20it%20each%20night%20at%20a%20certain%20time%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20remember%20that%20you%20always%20have%20a%20warm%2C%20cozy%20blanket%20ready%20and%20waiting%20for%20you.%20You%20can%20also%20program%20the%20times%20to%20turn%20the%20blanket%20off%20at%20a%20designated%20time%2C%20even%20better%20than%20an%20auto-shutoff%20because%20it%20gives%20you%20all%20the%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20true%20to%20its%20smart%20designation%2C%20this%20blanket%20also%20rated%20the%20most%20consistent%20in%20our%20testing%2C%20with%20the%20least%20temperature%20fluctuations%2C%20and%20achieved%20a%20comfortable%20top-end%20temp%20of%2084%20F.%20It%20had%20even%20heat%2C%20and%20the%20temperature%20zones%20responded%20well.%20The%20blanket%20is%20well%20made%20and%20fluffy%2C%20with%20a%20furry%20texture%20on%20the%20outside%20and%20a%20more%20fleece-like%20one%20inside%2C%20but%20it%20sheds%20a%20little%20bit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20weighted%3A%20Pure%20Enrichment%20WeightedWarmth%20Weighted%20Blanket%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221520%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20smiles%20while%20lounging%20under%20the%20Pure%20Enrichment%20WeightedWarmth%20weighted%20blanket%20on%20a%20bed%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65df9b2390413ab8e1d7a49b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221140%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETester%20James%20Brains%20bought%20a%20second%20Pure%20Enrichment%20WeightedWarmth%20weighted%20blanket%20because%20his%20wife%20and%20he%20loved%20the%20combination%20of%20heat%20and%20heft.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize(s)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2050%26quot%3B%20x%2060%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Micromink%20and%20sherpa%20shell%2C%20glass%20beads%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeat%20Settings%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%204%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAuto%20Shut%20Off%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Yes%2C%20after%202-hours%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWarranty%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%205-year%20limited%20warranty%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2013%20pounds%2C%20plush%20feel%2C%20heats%20to%20105%20degrees%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOnly%20available%20in%20one%20size%20and%20color%2C%20complicated%20wash%20directions%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20think%20electric%20blankets%20are%20cozy%2C%20wait%20until%20you%20add%20weight%20to%20the%20equation.%20The%20Pure%20Enrichment%20WeightedWarmth%20Weighted%20Throw%20Blanket%20combines%20the%20best%20of%20both%20worlds%2C%20making%20it%20the%20top%20electric%20option%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-weighted-blanket%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20weighted%20blanke%3C%2Fa%3Et%20guide.%20It's%20so%20comforting%20that%20when%20reporter%20James%20Brains%20tried%20testing%20it%2C%20his%20wife%20couldn't%20bear%20to%20part%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%2013-pound%20blanket%20features%20dual-sided%20comfort%20with%20plush%20sherpa%20on%20one%20side%20and%20micro%20mink%20on%20the%20other%20(we%20especially%20loved%20the%20sherpa%20side).%20While%20its%2052-inch-by-60-inch%20dimensions%20may%20not%20cover%20you%20from%20head%20to%20toe%2C%20it's%20ideal%20for%20snuggling%20up%20during%20your%20latest%20streaming%20binge.%20The%20weight%20comes%20from%20glass%20beads%2C%20offering%20just%20enough%20pressure%20to%20feel%20secure%20without%20being%20overwhelmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20heating%20function%20has%20four%20settings%20ranging%20from%20warm%20to%20high%2C%20with%20the%20highest%20setting%20quickly%20reaching%20a%20toasty%20105%20degrees.%20Safety%20features%20include%20a%20two-hour%20auto%20shut-off%2C%20and%20the%20generous%209-foot%20power%20cord%20means%20you%20won't%20need%20an%20extension%20cord%20to%20stay%20plugged%20in.%20Pure%20Enrichment%20backs%20its%20product%20with%20a%20reassuring%20five-year%20warranty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20drawback%20is%20the%20cleaning%20instructions%20are%20surprisingly%20complex%2C%20requiring%20a%206-inch-by-6-inch%20tag%20sewn%20into%20the%20blanket%20to%20explain%20them%20all.%20But%20given%20how%20rarely%20you'll%20need%20to%20clean%20it%2C%20this%20seems%20a%20small%20price%20to%20pay%20for%20such%20luxurious%20comfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%3Cp%3EChoosing%20an%20electric%20blanket%20combines%20the%20intricacies%20of%20searching%20for%20great%20bed%20linens%20with%20a%20functional%20electrical%20device.%20Moreover%2C%20Joel%20Hawk%2C%20principal%20engineering%20manager%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ul.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUL%20Solutions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20does%20third-party%20testing%20and%20certifications%20of%20electric%20blankets%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20always%20tell%20a%20lot%20just%20by%20looking%20at%20it.%20How%20well%20the%20internal%20heating%20elements%20work%20can%20be%20a%20mystery%20until%20you%20actually%20try%20them%20out.%26quot%3B%20Here%20are%20some%20factors%20to%20consider%20when%20researching%20your%20purchase%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b402a3d-25f8-433f-af1a-4e16cce2e70c%5C%22%3EThird-party%20certification%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20number%20one%20recommendation%20from%20experts%20is%20to%20check%20that%20the%20blanket%20has%20been%20inspected%20by%20an%20independent%20testing%20laboratory%2C%20which%20ensures%20that%20it%20meets%20established%20safety%20standards%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Susan%20McKelvey%2C%20communications%20manager%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nfpa.org%2Fen%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Fire%20Protection%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20guide%20examined%20brands%20with%20UL%2C%20Intertek%2C%20or%20CSA%20certification%2C%20popular%20third-party%20safety%20certifications%20for%20consumer%20goods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20can%20be%20tough%20to%20tell%20with%20online%20purchases%2C%20but%20the%20product%20packaging%20should%20have%20a%20certifier%20logo%20printed%20somewhere%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Hawk.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20an%20indication%20that%20a%20lab%20tested%20the%20product%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20meets%20a%20nationally%20recommended%20standard%20for%20similar%20products.%20Certification%20is%20voluntary%2C%20so%20if%20a%20product%20does%20not%20have%20it%2C%20you%20may%20be%20taking%20a%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2248c91454-615d-435a-916a-b41fdd4547b9%5C%22%3EAuto-shutoff%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20important%20safety%20consideration%20is%20an%20auto-shutoff%20feature%20or%20timer%2C%20which%20is%20useful%20should%20you%20want%20to%20sleep%20with%20your%20blanket.%20People%20always%20think%20of%20safety%20regarding%20electrical%20fires%2C%20said%20Hawk%2C%20but%20thermal%20burns%20from%20blankets%20set%20too%20high%20for%20too%20long%20are%20more%20common.%20Some%20heated%20blankets%20allow%20you%20to%20adjust%20the%20window%20of%20time%20the%20blanket%20remains%20on%20before%20auto-shutoff%20kicks%20in%2C%20so%20think%20about%20how%20long%20you%20will%20be%20using%20the%20blanket%20and%20whether%20you%20need%20flexibility%20in%20that%20feature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b5482e5-3d0c-4397-85d5-945fbe6e6323%5C%22%3EHeat%20level%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Hawk%2C%20national%20standards%20mandate%20that%20the%20surface%20temperature%20of%20a%20heated%20blanket%20may%20not%20exceed%20149%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%2C%20but%20our%20testing%20showed%20that%20most%20didn't%20even%20come%20close%20to%20being%20that%20hot.%20The%20temperature%20will%20be%20affected%20if%20a%20blanket%20is%20bunched%20up%20so%20that%20many%20wires%20converge%20in%20one%20place%3B%20however%2C%20it's%20best%20practice%20to%20lay%20a%20blanket%20as%20flat%20as%20possible%20and%20avoid%20doubling%20it.%20The%20blankets%20in%20our%20tests%20ranged%20from%203%20heat%20levels%20to%2012%2C%20so%20think%20about%20how%20sensitive%20you%20are%20to%20temperature%20and%20whether%20you%20want%20the%20ability%20to%20fine-tune%20it%20or%20are%20OK%20with%20simple%20controls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2225f03780-0cb1-4584-bd07-46d6330d88b7%5C%22%3ESpecial%20features%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20blankets%20come%20with%20auto-shutoff%20standards%2C%20but%20others%20have%20features%20that%20make%20them%20compatible%20with%20wifi%2C%20so%20they%20can%20be%20controlled%20remotely%20or%20have%20dual%20temperature%20zones%20to%20accommodate%20more%20than%20one%20user%20at%20a%20time.%20Consider%20what%20you'll%20use%20and%20what%20is%20worth%20paying%20for.%20Some%20brands%20also%20offer%20wearable%20designs%2C%20battery-operated%20models%20for%20outdoor%20use%2C%20and%20foot%20pockets%20to%20keep%20feet%20cozy.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2251953c2a-7fdb-46c8-ad3c-6adb0c3e3cf0%5C%22%3EMaterials%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20heated%20blankets%20are%20some%20form%20of%20polyester%20because%20it%20is%20inflammable%20and%20washable.%20But%20different%20blankets%20have%20different%20textures%2C%20so%20know%20if%20you%20want%20to%20cuddle%20up%20in%20something%20resembling%20flannel%20or%20feel%20cozier%20in%20a%20fleece%20or%20sherpa-style%20microfiber.%20The%20thickness%20of%20the%20fabric%20can%20also%20play%20a%20role%3A%20heavier%20blankets%20may%20make%20you%20feel%20too%20warm%20and%20are%20bulky%20to%20store%2C%20but%20too%20thin%20fabrics%20may%20have%20you%20noticing%20the%20heating%20wires.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b97d0b57-647c-41e7-b31c-8373ef2c8c74%5C%22%3ESize%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20want%20to%20consider%20not%20only%20the%20size%20and%20capacity%20of%20your%20blankets%2C%20which%20are%20available%20in%20throws%20and%20standard%20bedding%20sizes%20like%20twin%2C%20full%2C%20queen%2C%20and%20king%20sizes%20but%20also%20the%20cord.%20Shorter%20cords%20require%20you%20to%20use%20the%20blanket%20near%20an%20outlet%20and%20restrict%20movement.%20You'll%20also%20want%20to%20ensure%20the%20wires%20are%20evenly%20distributed%20throughout%2C%20especially%20in%20larger%20blankets%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20have%20cold%20spots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20electric%20blankets%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20selection%20of%20heated%20blanket%20boxes%20on%20a%20bed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6597007f1c5c7b8c9a0e0465%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20tested%20several%20different%20electric%20blankets%20and%20examined%20factors%20such%20as%20how%20well%20they%20maintained%20their%20temperature%2C%20comfort%2C%20and%20ease%20of%20use.%3Cp%3EJill%20Waldbieser%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20consulted%20Hawk%20and%20McKelvey%20about%20what%20to%20look%20for%20in%20an%20electric%20blanket%20and%20safety%20considerations.%20Based%20on%20those%20recommendations%2C%20we%20researched%20dozens%20of%20products%20on%20the%20market%20before%20choosing%20six%20to%20test.%20We%20used%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thermoworks.com%2Fir-gun%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThermoWorks%20infrared%20thermometer%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20verify%20temperature%20settings%20and%20how%20well%20each%20blanket%20held%20its%20temperature%20at%20one%2C%20two%2C%20and%20three%20hours%20and%20confirmed%20if%20the%20auto-shut-off%20worked.%20We%20machine-washed%20each%20blanket%20and%20re-tested%20it%20to%20compare%20performance%20and%20fabric%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EElectric%20Blanket%20FAQ%3Ch3%3EAre%20Electric%20blankets%20safe%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.esfi.org%2Felectric-blanket-fire-prevention%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHeating%2520pads%2520and%2520electric%2520blankets%2Cmore%2520than%2520ten%2520years%2520old.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElectrical%20Safety%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20electric%20blankets%20cause%20about%20500%20fires%20a%20year%2C%20and%20most%20of%20those%20are%20caused%20by%20older%20or%20improperly%20used%20products.%20Most%20electric%20blankets%20are%20perfectly%20safe%20when%20used%20according%20to%20manufacturer%20instructions.%20Don't%20use%20one%20if%20the%20cord%20is%20frayed%2C%20and%20avoid%20scrunching%20or%20doubling%20up%20the%20blanket%20to%20keep%20the%20wires%20from%20tangling%20or%20becoming%20damaged.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20electric%20blankets%20work%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20electric%20b