20her%20first%20home%20while%20still%20paying%20down%20her%20debt%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20wealth-building%20in%20mind.%20%26quot%3BI%20purchased%20in%20an%20area%20and%20in%20a%20building%20that%20I%20thought%20was%20undervalued%20that%20I%20knew%20would%20have%20higher%20levels%20of%20appreciation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20renting%20out%20the%20home%2C%20Victoria%20lived%20in%20it%20and%20waited%20while%20the%20value%20increased.%20%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20my%20main%20choice%3B%20it%20wasn't%20the%20home%20of%20my%20dreams.%20It%20was%20the%20home%20I%20knew%20would%20help%20me%20achieve%20my%20dreams%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20ended%20up%20selling%20the%20home%20two%20years%20later%20and%20making%20roughly%20150%2C000%20Canadian%20dollars%20from%20the%20sale.%20In%20Canada%2C%20where%20Victoria%20lives%2C%20there%20is%20a%20primary%20residence%20tax%20exemption%2C%20so%20she%20didn't%20pay%20taxes%20on%20the%20gains.%20She's%20used%20this%20strategy%20again%20with%20the%20property%20she%20lives%20in.%20%26quot%3BMost%20people%20don't%20think%20of%20their%20own%20property%20as%20a%20way%20to%20make%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVictoria%20also%20invests%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-an-etf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexchange-traded%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20look%20at%20buying%20individual%20stocks%2C%20I%20believe%20that's%20gambling%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20look%20at%20buying%20ETFs%20so%20that%20my%20money%20can%20make%20money%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c537d361-21dd-4d05-ab26-b9d1f7e8fc22%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShe%20lives%20below%20her%20means%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20achieving%20millionaire%20status%2C%20Victoria%20still%20has%20goals%20she%20hopes%20to%20meet%20with%20her%20money.%20She%20wants%20to