onsider%20adding%20other%20textures%20to%20your%20space%20to%20create%20more%20variety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMinimalism%20took%20over%20to%20a%20fault.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Living%20room%20with%20plain%20white%20walls%2C%20white%20couch%20and%20chair%20and%20acrylic%20coffee%20table%20on%20top%20of%20wood%20floors%20with%20beige%20area%20rug%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6761d8a0ccd8dfcfcd7fb271%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMinimalism%20can%20sometimes%20feel%20boring.%3Cp%3EProcreators%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETatsioni%20told%20us%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteps-to-become-more-minimalist-2017-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eminimalism%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20taken%20to%20extremes%20to%20create%20tidy%20and%20clean-looking%20spaces%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%20and%20isn't%20working%20in%20its%20current%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20many%20interiors%20are%20starting%20to%20look%20like%20those%20I'd%20find%20in%20a%20show%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BMinimalism%20can%20be%20done%20beautifully%2C%20but%20when%20brought%20to%20the%20extreme%2C%20it%20can%20dampen%20any%20sign%20of%20unique%20personality%20or%20character%20in%20an%20interior%2C%20making%20a%20place%20feel%20sterile%20and%20uninviting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOversized%20furniture%20in%20small%20spaces%20is%20a%20miss.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%229474%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerial%20view%20of%20large%20teal%20sectional%20couch%20in%20small%20living%20room%20with%20small%20square%20coffee%20table%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6761d81c1d90e3bcf31d6d0b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226316%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20giant%20couch%20won't%20really%20make%20your%20living%20room%20feel%20bigger.%3Cp%3EDa