ity%20to%20predominantly%20white%20spaces%20by%20%26quot%3Bincorporating%20colorful%20accents%20like%20throw%20pillows%2C%20artwork%2C%20or%20even%20a%20textured%20rug.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20industrial%20style%20didn't%20work%20in%20some%20living%20rooms%20this%20year.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224896%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brick%20room%20with%20plants%20hanging%20from%20ceiling%20and%20light%20fixtures%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6761d4b36c531c315b88d16a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223264%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrick%20walls%20can%20feel%20cold%20if%20they're%20not%20styled%20right.%3Cp%3EJuly%20Prokopiv%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIndustrial%20elements%20include%20metal%20accents%2C%20exposed%20bricks%2C%20and%20raw%20materials.%20They%20can%20make%20a%20space%20look%20edgy%20and%20modern.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20a%20living%20room%20leans%20too%20far%20into%20this%20design%20style%2C%20Smith%20said%2C%20it%20instead%20%26quot%3Bcomes%20off%20as%20cold%20and%20impersonal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20balanced%20approach%20using%20softer%20textures%20and%20natural%20materials%20can%20help%20soften%20the%20industrial%20feel%20and%20make%20the%20space%20more%20welcoming%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMaximalist%20patterns%2C%20colors%2C%20and%20styles%20didn't%20always%20work.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225499%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Living%20room%20with%20colorful%20blue%20wallpaper%2C%20blue%20velvet%20couch%2C%20plants%2C%20decorative%20chairs%2C%20and%20shelf%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6761d6e6ccd8dfcfcd7fb1e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223845%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20of%20the%20best%20maximalist%20spaces%20stick%20with%20a%20color%20scheme.%3Cp%3Eunited%20photo%20studio%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKeri%20Petersen%2C%20owner%20and%20lead%20designer%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkpspaces.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKP%20Spaces%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20maximalism%20missed%20the%20mark%20this%20year%20because%20it%20can%20quickly%20go%20from%20%26quot%3Bcollected%20and%20cool%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Bcluttered%20chaos%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20living%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToo%20many%20patterns%2C%20colors%2C%20and%20styles%20thrown%20together%20without%20a%20plan%3F%20The%20result%20is%20a%20space%20that%20feels%20overwhelming%20and%20anything%20but%20relaxing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmake-home-look-better-for-free-without-buying-anything%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadd%20life%20to%20a%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20creating%20chaos%2C%20she%20suggested%20sticking%20with%20a%20cohesive%20color%20palette%20and%20limiting%20yourself%20to%20only%20using%20two%20or%20three%20complementary%20patterns%20in%20a%20room.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20novelty%20of%20wood-paneled%20accent%20walls%20didn't%20last.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224405%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wood-paneled%20wall%20with%20simple%20beige%20couch%20and%20small%20round%20coffee%20table%20and%20side%20table%20in%20front%20of%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6761d6446c531c315b88d1f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222937%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EToo%20much%20wood%20can%20look%20dated.%3Cp%3EWashdog%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWood-paneled%20accent%20walls%20were%20a%20fun%20way%20to%20bring%20a%20natural%2C%20rustic%20touch%20into%20a%20home.%20But%2C%20like%20all%20trends%2C%20it%20got%20overdone%2C%20fast%2C%26quot%3B%20Petersen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20when%20too%20many%20walls%20are%20paneled%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20with%20cheap%2C%20f