er%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%2C%20Dr.%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20aged%2092.%20He%20was%20being%20treated%20for%20age-related%20medical%20conditions%20and%20had%20sudden%20loss%20of%20consciousness%20at%20home%20on%2026th%20December%202024.%20Resuscitative%20measures%20were%20started%20immediately%20at%20home.%20He%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20Medical%20Emergency%20at%20AIIMS%2C%20New%20Delhi%20at%208%3A06%20PM.%20Despite%20all%20efforts%2C%20he%20could%20not%20be%20revived%20and%20was%20declared%20dead%20at%209%3A51%20PM%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManmohan%20Singh's%20family%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flive-updates-manmohan-singh-hospitalised-at-aiims-family-reaches-hospital-7338179%5C%22%3Ereached%20the%20hospital%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20so%20did%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra.%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20are%20flying%20back%20to%20Delhi%20from%20Belagavi%20in%20Karnataka%20where%20they%20were%20attending%20a%20party%20event%20earlier%20in%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETributes%20poured%20in%20for%20the%20two-time%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20architect%20of%20India's%20economic%20reforms.%20Terming%20Manmohan%20Singh%20one%20of%20India's%20most%20distinguished%20leaders%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20the%20late%20Congress%20leader%20made%20extensive%20efforts%20to%20improve%20people's%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20mourns%20the%20loss%20of%20one%20of%20its%20most%20distinguished%20leaders%2C%20Dr.%20Manmohan%20Singh%20Ji.%20Rising%20from%20humble%20origins%2C%20he%20rose%20to%20become%20a%20respected%20economist.%20He%20served%20in%20various%20government%20positions%20as%20well%2C%20including%20as%20Finance%20Minister%2C%20leaving%20a%20strong%20imprint%20on%20our%20economic%20policy%20over%20the%20years.%20His%20interventions%20in%20Parliame