h%20and%20the%20period%20from%201991%20till%202014%20will%20be%20a%20golden%20chapter%20in%20the%20history%20of%20India.%20I%20worked%20closely%20with%20him%20for%20many%20years.%20I%20have%20not%20met%20a%20person%20more%20humble%20and%20self-effacing%20than%20Dr%20Singh.%20He%20wore%20his%20scholarship%20lightly%20and%20never%20claimed%20credit%20for%20any%20of%20his%20historic%20achievements.%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Chidambaram%2C%20now%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20finance%20minister%20under%20the%20then%20prime%20minister%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao%20(1991-1996)%2C%20was%20the%20architect%20and%20the%20brainchild%20of%20economic%20reforms%20in%201991%20that%20pulled%20India%20from%20the%20brink%20of%20bankruptcy%20and%20ushered%20in%20an%20era%20of%20economic%20liberalisation%20that%20is%20widely%20believed%20to%20have%20changed%20the%20course%20of%20India's%20economic%20trajectory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20story%20of%20India%20turned%20after%20Dr%20Singh%20became%20Finance%20Minister.%20And%20the%20present%20middle%20class%20of%20India%20was%20virtually%20the%20creation%20of%20his%20policies%20as%20Finance%20Minister%20and%20Prime%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Chidambaram%2C%20adding%20while%20the%20former%20Prime%20Minister's%20policies%20were%20liberal%20and%20progressive%2C%20he%20%26quot%3Bnever%20forgot%20the%20poor%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20examples%20of%20the%20former%20Prime%20Minister's%20%26quot%3Bsterling%20commitment%20to%20the%20poor%26quot%3B%2C%20P%20Chidambaram%20singled%20out%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20or%20MNREGA%2C%20a%20rural%20jobs%20guarantee%20scheme%2C%20and%20the%20restructuring%20of%20the%20Public%20Distribution%20System%20or%20PDS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThroughout%20his%20tenure%2C%20he%20had%20great%20empathy%20for%20the%20poor.%20He%20did%20not%20hide%20the%20fact%20that%20many%20million