ake%20Lively%2C%20who%20played%20Lily%20Bloom%20in%20Justin%20Baldoni's%3Cem%3E%20It%20Ends%20With%20Us%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20has%20accused%20her%20co-star%20Baldoni%20of%20sexual%20misconduct%20in%20an%2080-page%20complaint.%20Her%20complaint%20against%20Baldoni%2C%20and%20Jamey%20Heath%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Baldoni's%20production%20studio%20Wayfarer%2C%20accuses%20the%20two%20men%20of%20repeated%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20other%20disturbing%20behaviour%20on%20the%20set%20of%20%3Cem%3EIt%20Ends%20With%20Us%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20Blake%20Lively%2C%20other%20crew%20members%20too%20fell%20prey%20to%20Justin%20Baldoni's%20misconduct%20and%20had%20also%20spoken%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELively%20had%20raised%20objection%20to%20Baldoni%20and%20Heath%20making%20%26quot%3Bsexually%20inappropriate%20jokes%26quot%3B%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20a%20plethora%20of%20other%20accusations.%20The%20studio%20agreed%20to%20have%20an%20intimacy%20coordinator%20on%20board%20and%20not%20retaliate%20against%20Lively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20meeting%20was%20held%20on%20January%204%20this%20year%2C%20where%C2%A0the%20following%20code%20of%20conduct%20was%20decided%2C%20to%20allow%20a%20safe%20and%20protected%20environment%20during%20the%20shoot%20of%20%3Cem%3EIt%20Ends%20With%20Us%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20more%20shocking%20of%20allegations%20that%20Blake%20Lively%20had%20in%20her%2080-page%20complaint%20are%20the%20following%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJustin%20Baldoni%20and%20Jamey%20Heath%20made%20lewd%2C%20sexual%20comments%2C%20and%20showed%20Blake%20Lively%20nude%20images%20of%20other%20women%2C%20including%20Heath's%20wife.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBaldoni%20and%20Heath%20spoke%20about%20their%20previous%20%26quot%3Bpornography%20addiction%26quot%3B%20and%20Blake%20Lively's%20lack%20of%20pornography%20consumption%20to%20her%20and%20to%20other%20crew%20members.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThey%20also%20discussed%20with%20Blake%20and%20her%20employees%20about%20their%20personal%20experiences%20with%20sex%2C%20including%20as%20it%20relates%20to%20spouses%20or%20others.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMention%20to%20BL%20or%20her%C2%A0employees%20of%20personal%20times%20that%20physical%20consent%20was%20not%20given%20in%20sexual%20acts%2C%20as%20either%20the%20abuser%20or%20the%20abused.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20accused%20described%20Blake's%20genitalia%20to%20her.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThey%20also%20made%20jokes%20and%20disparaging%20comments%20at%20Lively's%20expense.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBaldoni%20also%20allegedly%20called%20up%20Lively's%20trainer%20to%20ask%20about%20her%20weight.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBaldoni%2C%20on%20set%2C%20claimed%20to%20%26quot%3Bspeak%C2%A0to%26quot%3B%20Lively's%20recently%C2%A0dead%20father.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBaldoni%20pressed%20for%20Lively%20to%20disclose%20her%20religious%20beliefs%2C%20and%20shared%20his.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBL%20and%2For%20her%20infant%20were%20exposed%20to%20COVID%20and%20not%20informed.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENo%20intimacy%20coordinator%20was%20on%20set%20in%20scenes%20with%20Baldoni.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20was%20personal%2C%20physical%20touching%20of%2C%20and%20sexual%20comments%20by%2C%20Baldoni%20and%20Heath%20to%20Blake%20Lively%20and%C2%A0her%20employees%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20female%20cast%20or%20crew%20without%20their%20express%20consent.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBaldoni%20improvised%20kissing%20scenes%2C%20bit%C2%A0and%20sucked%20Lively's%20lip%C2%A0without%20her%20consent.%20In%20addition%2C%20he%20also%20had%20several%20intimate%20conversations%20with%20Blake%20as%20Baldoni%2C%20and%20not%20Ryle%20Kincaid%2C%20his%20on-screen%20character.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBlake%20had%20no%20representative%C2%A0on%20set%20or%20with%20a%20monitor%20during%20scenes%C2%A0involving%20nudity%2C%20sexual%20activity%2C%20or%20violence%20with%20Baldoni.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBaldoni%20called%20his%20friend%20to%20play%20the%20doctor%20who%20assists%20Liv