ots%20of%20countless%20stars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20second%20day%2C%20we%20trek%20up%20to%20Kala%20Pokhari%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sasang%20informs.%20A%20slightly%20larger%20establishment%2C%20Kala%20Pokhari%20is%20named%20after%20the%20seemingly%20black%20lake%20it%20houses%20(%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EKala%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20meaning%20black%20and%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EPokhari%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20meaning%20lake%20in%20Nepali).%20At%20an%20altitude%20of%203%2C000%20metres%20(9%2C842%20feet)%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20perfect%20place%20to%20rest%20and%20take%20in%20the%20breathtaking%20surroundings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fs2_11zon-1735043656.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20outline%20of%20the%20Kanchendzonga%20range%20resembling%20'The%20Sleeping%20Buddha'%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fs2_11zon-1735043656.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fs2_11zon-1735043656-300x138.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fs2_11zon-1735043656-500x230.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fs2_11zon-1735043656-768x354.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fs2_11zon-1735043656-1536x708.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fs2_11zon-1735043656-150x69.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-392130%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22737%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20outline%20of%20the%20Kanchendzonga%20range%20resembling%20%E2%80%98The%20Sleeping%20Buddha%E2%80%99%3B%20Image%3A%20Jacob%20Subba%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20after