%80%99s%20your%20choice%20whether%20you%20want%20to%20reach%20Phalut%20or%20climb%20down%20through%20Rimbik%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sasang%20says.%20The%20descent%20from%20the%20summit%20ends%20in%20the%20town%20of%20Rimbik%20and%20passes%20through%20Sirikhola.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhalut%2C%20the%20second-highest%20peak%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20remains%20a%20popular%20spot%20among%20trekkers%20due%20to%20its%20pristine%20location%2C%20breathtaking%20views%2C%20and%20colour%20tapestry%20created%20by%20full-bloom%20rhododendrons.%20Many%20believe%20that%20the%20trek%20to%20Sandakphu%20is%20incomplete%20without%20setting%20foot%20on%20Phalut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241201-WA0013-1735044127-500x667.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20sunset%20paints%20a%20silhouette%20of%20jeeps%20near%20Sandakphu%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241201-WA0013-1735044127-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241201-WA0013-1735044127-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241201-WA0013-1735044127-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241201-WA0013-1735044127-1152x1536.jpg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241201-WA0013-1735044127-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241201-WA0013-1735044127-150x200.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241201-WA0013-1735044127.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-392141%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22