ppreciates%20our%20organic%20vegetables%2C%20knowing%20they%20are%20sourcing%20them%20for%20their%20cancer-ridden%20parents%20or%20their%20pregnant%20wives.%20I%20might%20not%20be%20earning%20as%20much%20since%20leaving%20Google%2C%20but%20money%20eventually%20follows.%20I%E2%80%99m%20glad%20I%E2%80%99m%20making%20good%20use%20of%20my%20time%20and%20skills%20while%20improving%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives%2C%20so%20I%E2%80%99m%20truly%20enjoying%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Mantaj%20Sidhu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735029186000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fgill-organics-1-1735016918.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D391908%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mantaj%20Sidhu%20quit%20his%20high-paying%20Google%20job%20in%20Ireland%20to%20start%20Gill%20Organics%2C%20a%20venture%20that%20lets%20urban%20families%20temporarily%20own%20a%20patch%20of%20land%20where%20fresh%2C%20organic%20food%20is%20grown%20for%20them.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20he%20is%20bridging%20the%20gap%20in%20demand%20and%20supply%20of%20chemical-free%20produce.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F391908%2Ftechie-quit-google-job-returns-india-to-do-organic-farming-helps-families-access-chemical-free-food-gill-organics%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Learnt%20More%20Than%20I%20Did%20in%20School%E2%80%99%3A%20What%20Homeschooling%20for%205%20Years%20Taught%20Me%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20much%20of%20what%20you%20studied%20in%20school%20do%20you%20put%20to%20use%20in%20life%3F%E2%80%9D%20Hyderabad-based%20Vaishnavi%20Anantha%20(17)%20asks%20me.%20She%20takes%20my%20silence%20as%20a%20cue%20to%20go%20on.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20spend%20eight%20hours%20a%20day%20in%20school%2C%20bu