0%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20now%20been%20five%20years%20of%20homeschooling%20and%20in%20hindsight%2C%20Vaishnavi%20recalls%20it%20as%20her%20best%20decision.%20%E2%80%9CWork%20life%20will%20anyway%20come%20with%20its%20pressures.%20I%20did%20not%20want%20my%20school%20life%20to%20be%20stressful%20too.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderscoring%20the%20benefits%20of%20this%20radical%20approach%2C%20psychologist%20Varkha%20Chulani%20says%20the%20model%20permits%20control%20over%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F274602%2Fteacher-homeschools-children-shares-tips-fun-syllabus-social-skills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edistribution%20of%20time%20across%20subjects%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20the%20parent%20can%20supervise%20if%20the%20child%20pays%20equal%20attention%20to%20Sanskrit%20as%20he%20would%20to%20Maths.%20Conversely%2C%20if%20a%20parent%20sees%20that%20a%20child%20can%20excel%20in%20Science%20and%20Maths%2C%20he%20or%20she%20can%20stress%20more%20on%20it.%E2%80%9D%20While%20allowing%20for%20substantive%20attention%20to%20core%20competencies%2C%20it%20also%20enables%20children%20to%20explore%20their%20other%20strengths.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EYour%20questions%20on%20homeschooling%20answered%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20Monday%20morning%20when%20I%20speak%20to%20Vaishnavi.%20An%20ironic%20time%20to%20catch%20a%20student%20who%20would%2C%20in%20a%20traditional%20reality%2C%20be%20in%20her%20first%20or%20second%20class%20of%20the%20day.%20But%20this%20student%20is%20relaxed%20and%20composed%2C%20surrounded%20by%20her%20books%2C%20and%20blank%20sheets%20of