C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vaishnavi%20Anantha%20has%20written%20four%20novels%20during%20the%20time%20she%20homeschooled%20and%20these%20are%20part%20of%20The%20JAZ%20Gang%20series%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhomeschooling-Vaishnavi-Anantha-1733909413.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhomeschooling-Vaishnavi-Anantha-1733909413-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhomeschooling-Vaishnavi-Anantha-1733909413-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhomeschooling-Vaishnavi-Anantha-1733909413-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhomeschooling-Vaishnavi-Anantha-1733909413-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388438%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVaishnavi%20Anantha%20has%20written%20four%20novels%20during%20the%20time%20she%20homeschooled%20and%20these%20are%20part%20of%20The%20JAZ%20Gang%20series.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20did%20you%20know%20it%20was%20time%20to%20homeschool%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20sit%20for%20hours%20in%20front%20of%20the%20screen%20for%20lectures.%20After%20class%2C%20we%20would%20be%20back%20again%20in%20front%20of%20the%20screen%20to%20complete%20our%20homework.%20It%20was%20stressful.%E2%80%9D%20Being%20an%20outdoor%20girl%20who%20loved%20sports%2C%20Vaishnavi%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20habituated%20to%20so%20much%20screen%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThings%20peaked%20after%20one%20particular%20Maths%20class%20when%2C%20after%20spending%20hours%20learning%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F270005%2Fmaths-in-indian-monuments-ancient-science-symmetry-architecture-heritage%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20geometry%20concept%20%3C%2Fa%3Eonline%2C%20Vaishnavi%20still%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20make%20head%20nor%20tail%20of%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20the%20day%20she%20told%20her%20parents%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20just%20can%E2%80%99t%20do%20it.%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20learning%20anything.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20homeschooling%20mean%20waking%20up%20late%20and%20doing%20what%20you%20please%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20laughs%20Vaishnavi.%20She%20recalls%20her%20parents%E2%80%99%20firm%20instructions%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CYou%20need%20to%20utilise%20your%20time%20properly%2C%20follow%20a%20timetable%20and%20be%20disciplined.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20wake%20up%20early.%20Then%20exercise%20for%20an%20hour.%E2%80%9D%20The%20black%20belt%20in%20taekwondo%20(a%20form%20of%20martial%20arts)%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20miss%20out%20on%20her%20exercise%20regime.%20%E2%80%9CThen%20I%20would%20study%20for%20the%20next%20four%20hours%2C%20followed%20by%20YouTube%20sessions%20to%20catch%20up%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330277%2Fbengaluru-startup-stemonsters-founder-dr-sonali-dasgupta-making-science-fun-for-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20experiments%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20parents%20ensured%20that%20everything%20I%20learnt%20was%20in%20sync%20with%20what%20was%20being%20taught%20in%20school.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20afternoons%2C%20the%20young%20writer%20sat%20to%20work%20on%20her%20novels%2C%20followed%20by%20play%20sessions%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20and%20a%20round-up%20on%20the%20daily%20news%20at%20night.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20what%20do%20you%20do%20with%20all%20the%20extra%20time%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20use%20it%20to%20find%20out%20what%20you%E2%80%99re%20good%20at%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vaishnavi%20says.%20For%20instance%2C%20she%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20never%20an%20avid%20reader%20or%20writer.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20her%20curiosity%20was%20piqued%20when%20her%20mother%20assigned%20her%20a%20few%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F302842%2Fchildren-book-recommendations-by-indian-authors-ruskin-bond-chitra-banerjee-anu-kumar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreative%20writing%3C%2Fa%3E%20passages%20one%20day.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20where%20I%20developed%20an%20interest%20in%20writing.%20I%20used%20my%20time%20to%20watch%20relevant%20videos%2C%20develop%20a%20storyline%20for%20my%20books%2C%20and%20research%20the%20India%20of%20the%20past%2C%20people%E2%80%99s%20way%20of%20life%2C%20the%20food%20habits%20and%20the%20accommodation.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FFzpm4jWhF1g%3Fsi%3DsXQ-DWwHgiyzyL0M%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20homeschooling%20make%20you%20introverted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidering%20you%20aren%E2%80%99t%20expected%20to%20dress%20up%20and%20go%20to%20school%2C%20participate%20in%20school%20events%2C%20have%20annual%20days%20or%20sports%20days%20to%20channel%20your%20energies%20in%2C%20there%20is%20an%20understandable%20tendency%20to%20retreat%20into%20a%20shell.%20But%20this%20is%20where%2C%20Vaishnavi%20says%2C%20your%20hobbies%20will%20play%20a%20role.%20%E2%80%9CWriting%20has%20helped%20me%20tremendously%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20skills%2C%20from%20designing%20the%20book%20cover%20to%20creating%20video%20trailers%20on%20my%20own.%20It%20has%20also%20forced%20me%20to%20come%20out%20of%20my%20introverted%20nature%20to%20promote%20my%20books%20on%20various%20platforms.%E2%80%9D%20She%20recalls%20participating%20in%20prestigious%20literary%20events%2C%20including%20three%20appearances%20at%20the%20National%20Hyderabad%20Book%20Fair%20and%20a%20chance%20to%20speak%20at%20the%20%E2%80%98Youngistan%20Nukkad%E2%80%99%20at%20the%20Hyderabad%20Literature%20Festival%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContending%20the%20assumption%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F262348%2Findia-homeschooling-tips-guidance-success-board-exams-marks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehomeschoolers%20%3C%2Fa%3Edon%E2%80%99t%20have%20friends%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20often%20think%20that%20homeschooling%20means%20an%20end%20to%20socialisation.%20But%20I%20tell%20them%20that%20I%20have%20gotten%20a%20lot%20more%20time%20to%20socialise%20after%20homeschooling.%20I%20have%20more%20friends%20now%20than%20I%20did%20in%20school.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20part%20about%20being%20homeschooled%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20teaches%20one%20%E2%80%98life%20skills%2C%E2%80%99%20a%20thing%20many%20schools%20don%E2%80%99t%2C%20Vaishnavi%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20the%20curriculum%20my%20parents%20curated%2C%20I%20would%20wake%20up%20early%2C%20exercise%2C%20recite%20%3Cem%3Eshlokas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(religious%20scripture)%20and%20wash%20my%20clothes%20despite%20having%20a%20washing%20machine.%20If%20the%20house%20help%20didn%E2%80%99t%20arrive%2C%20I%20would%20help%20my%20mom%20wash%20the%20utensils%20and%20even%20sweep%20and%20mop%20the%20floor.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20anyone%20wondering%20if%20homeschooling%20could%20be%20their%20cup%20of%20tea%2C%20Vaishnavi%20urges%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99ll%20never%20know%20until%20you%20try.%20When%20I%20was%20in%20school%2C%20I%20was%20externally%20motivated%20to%20get%20high%20grades%20as%20I%20wanted%20to%20maintain%20a%20good%20reputation%20with%20my%20peers%20and%20meet%20the%20expectations%20of%20my%20teachers.%20But%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F239943%2Fhyderabad-tata-nano-road-trip-homeschool-how-to-cherrapunji-learning-travel-icse-nios-inspirational-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20home-schooler%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20show%20off%20or%20prove%20anything%20to%20anyone.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESumming%20up%20her%20journey%20with%20homeschooling%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20learn%20because%20I%20like%20to.%20I%20learn%20because%20I%20want%20to.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.careers360.com%2F72000-indian-children-home-schooling-schooled-samagra-shiksha-abhiyan-ssa-education-ministry-monsoon-session-parliament%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOver%2072%2C000%20Indian%20children%20receiving%20home%20schooling%3A%20Education%20Ministry%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Atul%20Krishna%2C%20Published%20on%207%20August%202023.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Flife-style%2Frelationships%2Fparenting%2Fpros-on-cons-of-home-schooling%2Farticleshow%2F46985033.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPros%20on%20cons%20of%20home%20schooling%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%2